  <brief_title>Comparison Between Propofol-remifentanil Total Intravenous Anesthesia and Desflurane-remifentanil Balanced Anesthesia With Regard to Post-anesthetic Functional Recovery Measured With QoR-40</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
